{
  "texts": [
    "Our overarching objective revolves around delving into state-of-the-art research on fairness concerns, prompting an exploration of the involved researchers and their geographic affiliations within this research domain.",
    "This exploration encompasses their resolved challenges, methodologies employed, prospective research avenues, and experimental tools or datasets.",
    "Consequently, we have formalized the ensuing research questions (RQs):i.",
    "What is the state-of-the-art research on fairness issues in AI? ii.",
    "Which countries and individuals are the most engaged in this field of study? iii."
  ]
}